title: Amazon-Kindle_4.2.0.34.apk
description:
The newest version of Kindle for Android released:

August 12, 2013.


Enjoy reading books on your Android Tablet or Phone, including thousands of free Kindle books. The Kindle app puts over a million books at your fingertips. It's the app for every reader, whether you're a book reader, magazine reader, or newspaper reader, and you don't need to own a Kindle to use it. Choose from over a million Kindle books from the Kindle Store or enjoy popular magazines like The Economist and Reader's Digest with high-resolution color images.


Enjoy reading!
